ons signify a more complex magnetic\nstructure both at zero and finite fields for Mn1/3NbS2 than for the\nwell-investigated Cr1/3NbS2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 May 2019 19:07:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
