th, this is identified as the conformal\ncurvature (the Schwarzian derivative of the Frenet curvature); it is constant\nalong equilibrium curves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 May 2019 20:46:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 20:33:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-27"}
