eory. It has nothing to do with existence or\nnonexistence of dark energy and therefore for explaining cosmological\nacceleration dark energy is not needed. The result is obtained without using\nthe notion of dS background space (in particular, its metric and connection)\nbut simply as a consequence of quantum mechanics based on the dS Lie algebra.\nTherefore, $\\Lambda$ has a physical meaning only on classical level and the\ncosmological constant problem and the dark energy problem do not arise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 04:00:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 06:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2019 03:42:16 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2020 03:59:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-06"}
